 src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /><br /><br />If you look in the source folder the sprite of the arrows, they should look grey with a white border.  <br /><br />There are lots of awesome tracker songs, but most of them use a lot of channels <img src="./images/smilies/icon_sad.gif" alt=":(" title="Sad" /></div>

