						<div class="postbody">You might have to composite the text into sprite tiles yourself. Years ago, blargg and I wrote a 6502 variable width font (VWF) library that might be useful for something like this. The source code for this library is in vwf_draw.s in RHDE and the Action 53 menu.</div>

