					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">Mills wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Then, How can i use the consoleDrawText function from pvsneslib to write text in sprites?</div><br />You can't.<br />You need to put your text into a table, according to the tiles of your text and then transfert it to VRAM after a vblank.<br />Just take a look in pvsneslib in vbl function, you will see how I send text to vram during a vblank (it is in console.c, in consoleVblank function).</div>

